FW OU Presentation Cc Reminder Original Message From Herasimchuk Alyse Sent Friday September AM To Mcconnell Mike Crook Jody Moon Eric Scribner James OMalley Justin Lowell Thomas Miles Andrew Avila Rafael McConnell Mark Cc Elliott Lexi Johnson Shawna Subject OU Presentation Attached is the event sheet for the OU Presentation Please call if you have any questions Alyse Herasimchuk Recruiting Coordinator Enron Associate Analyst Programs Smith Street EB B Houston Texas Direct Fax

MBA Program Information Presentation Houston Cc Please join Dean George Daly Associate Dean Mary Miller and area alumni to learn about the unique educational and professional opportunities available to you at New York University Stern School of Business MBA Program Information Presentation Houston Wednesday September pm Enron Smith Street Houston TX Room EB C Special thanks to Enron for generously sponsoring this event Space is limited and will be filled in order of response Please RSVP by Monday September via email fax or our Web site Fax Please provide the following information Name Daytime Phone Email Address Evening Phone Email Please include the city name as the subject and your name daytime telephone number and email address in the message Web site wwwsternnyuedumbaadmissionsfulltimerecruit Click on RSVP Please include the city name as the subject and your name daytime telephone number and email address in the message Note Please email me also so I may get a correct head count on who is attending Thanks Alyse Herasimchuk Recruiting Coordinator Enron Associate Analyst Programs Smith Street EB B Houston Texas Direct Fax Embedded Picture Metafile
